{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"“八一”之歌","authors":["贺敬之"],"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":7,"day":26}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“八一”之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贺敬之当一场历史的暴风雨刚刚过去——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那难忘的战斗呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚写下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难忘的记忆……当伟大的进军从祝捷之时又已开始："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身后——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里长征，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼前——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长征万里！……——就在此时此际，我们迎来一九七七年光辉的“八一”——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里晴空呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘扬着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们灿烂的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军旗！……一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我仰望你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我扑向你——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席亲手创建的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大军队呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自人民的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我带枪的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级兄弟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在节日的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼声中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向你举起——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请接受我呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个“地方同志”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个老兵的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬礼！……——虽然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小八路”的军衣从我身上早已脱去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老红军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抚摸过的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的头顶呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今已被"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白发侵袭……但是，我的心呵永远在我们军中——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在毛主席、华主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"率领我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行列里！我的生命永远属于我们党、我们阶级——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也永远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"属于你！我仰望你，我扑向你——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千山万水的思念，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五湖四海的回忆……呵，南昌城头，破晓的枪声呵——井冈山顶烛天的火炬！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你照亮旧中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血染的大地呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"止住了亿万母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长夜的哭泣……“找红军去！……”“找红军去！……”——有多少前辈父兄，在呼喊你呵，奔向你！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“找八路军去！……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“找八路军去！……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——我这个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤脚少年呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和千万同辈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在日夜追赶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的足迹……不论是战争年代那滚滚的硝烟，还是这建设时期阵阵风雨……——你永远在召唤着我呵，一步步，一句句：“冲上前去！……”“冲上前去！……”二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，在我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亿万军民的心中呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大军队的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"司令部里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光辉的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远不落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿烂的群星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长明不熄……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的领袖和导师呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们伟大的统帅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们伟大的军队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是您呵亲手培育，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您永远在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指挥我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从胜利——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走向胜利！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在您的身旁——有伟大的战友呵，五十年来并肩站立——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步步紧跟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚定不移……呵，在我的这支歌里，我骄傲地唱着您们的名字："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的周总理——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的周副主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的朱总司令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶副主席、邓副主席！我唱着我们敬爱的刘帅、徐帅、聂帅呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我唱着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民怀念的元帅——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罗荣桓、贺龙、陈毅……您们的名字呵，和毛主席、华主席连在一起，和千百个董存瑞、亿万个雷锋呵连在一起——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，我们阶级大军的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿烂的太阳系！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无限自豪呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫敌人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无比畏惧……呵，从我听见第一声叫我“小鬼”呵在王家坪的司令部里……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到五十周年的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天的“八一”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我以“老兵”的名义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向您们敬礼——您们的名字呵，在我心中永远、永远闪耀呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教育我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为做一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真正的战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋斗不息！……任凭林贼用怎样的阴谋，“四人帮”匪徒施何种毒计——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"休想遮掩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您们永恒的光辉；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"片刻不能"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从人民心中把您们夺去！三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，暴风雨中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们灿烂的军旗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我仰望你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我扑向你——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对敌人："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满腔的怒火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捷报来时："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾盆的泪雨……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老首长呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老同志……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我至亲的骨肉呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级的兄弟！——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"换穿的草鞋呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"替补的军衣……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰苦的岁月——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是多么的甜蜜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任“四人帮”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去追查什么“老关系”吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"批判什么“旧情绪”——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的同志呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是亲密！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的情谊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们永远呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远牢记！——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，宝塔山下，延水声里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指导员，你继续讲呵，讲呵！你们经过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少战斗到达遵义？——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽救了革命呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周副主席、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱总司令"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样坚定地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在一起……呵，老班长你接着讲呵，讲呵！你们怎样征服了雪山草地——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张国焘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是怎样叛变？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱总司令、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周副主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在如何斥敌？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶参谋长呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样在危急之中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫毛主席……呵，黄河渡口，雪里雨里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"司令员呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我身背米袋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在送你追你、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追你赶你呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里南下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那飞奔的马蹄……平津战场，烟里火里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老团长呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在前沿阵地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你将我扶起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你胸口的鲜血呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洒满我全身军衣……淮海战场，指挥部里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邓政委呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你钢铁的声音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞越千里硝烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震响在——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心里……呵，多少次会师——又誓师……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少回呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相逢——又别离……回音壁在回响万里军号……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五指山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又指向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"征程万里……呵，半个世纪我们的军史，代代鲜血染红的军旗！你字字行行丝丝缕缕——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都用毛泽东思想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在写呵："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们——胜利！”……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们——胜利！”……四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，暴风雨中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们血染的军旗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我仰望你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我扑向你——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿辈的幸福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父辈的感激……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们伟大的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民军队呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的红色江山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卫护在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的襟怀里！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门城楼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你的肩上呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巍然屹立！……你踏上继续革命的新的征程——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又投入"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化大革命的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大战役！我看见：多少老战友走上新阵地——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在路线斗争的战场："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百万战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里转战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年风雨……我看见：我们的老帅呵，在毛主席身边，和周总理一起，在滚滚激流中挺身而立——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提挈三军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋战鬼蜮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白发红心呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“青山夕照”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜似晨曦……我看见：永生的雷锋呵，在匍匐前进！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“硬骨头六连”呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向逆流迎击！在粉碎刘少奇、林彪、“四人帮”——一次次的大搏斗里："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我激跳的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似当年一样呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在日夜倾听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾听我军——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利消息……永远战斗的我们的军旗！你在军史的新篇章里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用鲜红的字迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写崭新的课题，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍然是呵："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们——胜利！”……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们——胜利！”……五呵，暴风雨中我们永不变色的军旗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一九七六年的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪水和怒火中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又铭刻下——七六年：那罕见的——艰难呵，七六年：那罕见的——胜利！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，我们的老政委呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然你向我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经常提起——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来之不易。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要懂得："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事业的艰巨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道路的崎岖……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我这个后来的战士呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也多少知道——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在前进途中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应随时准备"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不测的风雨……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怎能料到呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一生中的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一年里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟有如此"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悲痛的记忆？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一月——八日……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月——六日……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九月——九日……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，我们祖国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战火飞去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"礼花升起的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无边大地——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟会这样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被淹没在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪水的海洋里……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"司令员呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你这钢铁的战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨日还在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给我激励：为人民的欢乐放声歌唱呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今却是："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬雪……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋雨……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里长街"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同声哭泣……从天安门前，到万里营地——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们三军战士呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和人民一起——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同声——哭泣！……呵，就在此时此际，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这样的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“四人帮”拔刀出鞘！向我们党步步进逼——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"按他们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"篡党夺权的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“既定方针”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直逼——党中央，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直逼——华主席！反革命的“过河卒”，在杀向我们的将帅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“放火烧荒”的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罪恶火舌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舔向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的军旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——党旗！……乌云笼罩天空——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强震"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇撼大地……呵，远程而来的南湖的航船呵，此刻你将——驶向哪里？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新中国呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向何处去？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何处去？……六呵，暴风雨中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们更加鲜艳的军旗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此时此际，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这样的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们伟大的军队呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怎能不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十倍、百倍地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想念你？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“找红军去！……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“找八路军去！……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——这遥远的喊声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我少年时的回忆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能不从"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中涌起？……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟随"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八亿人民的心呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在暴风雨中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向你——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞去！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼唤你——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们党的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁臂膀呵！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们人民的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忠诚子弟！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼唤你——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们阶级的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁拳！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们专政的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柱石！”……我们呼唤你呵，我们想念你！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想念你呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信赖你！……我们的心带着——刘胡兰烈士当年的愤怒呵，戎冠秀大娘今天的焦虑……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从井冈山……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狼牙山……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里万里扑向你！我们看见呵，你带着——大渡河勇士当年的呼号，珍宝岛战士今天的誓词……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的心呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和我们一起——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遵义的风暴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庐山的霹雳……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起来到呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来到这里——在这中南海怒涛翻卷的红墙下——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级大搏斗的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"核心阵地……我们的民心、党心和军心呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集结在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在华国锋同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗飘飘的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸怀中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在叶副主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雷滚滚的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣襟里！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当两双巨手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握在一起……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这伟大的时刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再次证明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的真理——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的军队"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的手里！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民——心里！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又有了新的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英明领袖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的军队"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又有了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英明统帅——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周总理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱总司令呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不曾离去……贺龙同志，陈毅同志呵，您们就在这里！……——一九七六年这伟大的战役！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，伟大的开始呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的继续——我们的党史、军史又在华主席笔下——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用大字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"续写："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们——胜利！”……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们——胜利！”……我们——胜利呵，我们——胜利！胜利——在五十年漫漫的征途中，胜利——在未来崭新的世纪里……我看见——一九八七……一九九七……二○○七……每年的“八一”——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未来的战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍象今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们这样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满含着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热泪和感激，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰望你呵，扑向你！用全部热血和生命去迎接新的战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用全部热血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和生命呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把你高高举起……呵，你——毛泽东思想的伟大红旗！中国人民不朽的军旗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举着你呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举着你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和全世界的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级弟兄一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去夺取全人类"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彻底解放的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后——胜——利！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九七七年七月"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"贺龙","type":"人物"},{"name":"陈毅","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"四人帮","type":"人物"},{"name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}